After importing the app, the following connections need to be created.

Office 365 Outlook
  SharePoint List [Your Site] Documents
  SharePoint List [Your Site] KPI
  SharePoint List [Your Site] Setup
  SharePoint List [Your Site] Theme
  SharePoint List [Your Site] Grades
  SharePoint List [Your Site] Staff
  SharePoint List [Your Site] Users
  Apply Action to Button >> Select KPI Logo Upload (your flow should be created as per the name provided)

Once successful, the app will be ready for use.
